Subtract scopeOverhead cost times the number of descendant nodes from the inclusive time of each node.

detaileddescription.para: If numDescendantNodes is not null, add the number of nodes descendant to this node (not including this node) to *numDescendantNodes. Also for any nodes with descendants that are "noisy" wrt timerQuantum, do not subtract their times from the parent's exclusive time, but instead set their times to zero. This way we retain the sample count, but do not pollute the parent node's exclusive time with noise.
